1. install kolla-ansible
2. config openstack local repository
3. config update docker
4. config kolla-ansible
5. create ceph pool for openstack
6. set ceph pool for openstack and update globals.yaml
7. config kolla-ansible multinode  
8. kolla-ansible -i multinode prechecks
9. kolla-ansible -i multinode deploy
10.kolla-ansible post-deploy
11.sh init-runonce to deploy networking
12.kolla-ansible -i multinode destroy --include-images --yes-i-really-really-mean-it
